 libmtca4u-deviceaccess-dev (<< @mtca4u-deviceaccess_NEXT_SOVERSION@),
 dev-mtca4u-motordrivercard (>= @MotorDriverCard_VERSION@), dev-mtca4u-motordrivercard (<< @MotorDriverCard_NEXT_SOVERSION@),
